      "writtenOn": "2017-10-12T14:25:34Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thinking about this some more, we really need the texture to have 1 ref and no outstanding reads or writes here. The one caller has already guaranteed that, but who knows if this will prove useful for other callers. Perhaps we can rename (and change) this function to require this condition. Having a pure unique() function on a GrGpuResource might be a bit misleading since there are also pending IOs and the cache which can keep it alive after the ref is removed.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 62,
        "startChar": 8,
        "endLine": 62,
        "endChar": 26
      },
